The paper deals with wireless networks and throughput, which are topics commonly studied in the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a metric and algorithm, which are related to system design and control, respectively, and thus could fall under the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques, which could place it under the Multimedia (cs.MM) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
